Lua hacked port for the Milkymist board, move to  src/ and just type:

 git checkout milkymist
 make rtems RTEMS_MAKEFILE_PATH=/opt/rtems-4.11/lm32-rtems4.11/milkymist RTEMS_INC=/opt/rtems-4.11/lm32-rtems4.11/milkymist/lib/include/
 ~/milkymist/tools/flterm --port /dev/ttyUSB0 --kernel luam


If you want see changes:

 git diff  master...milkymist

